{"tid":701240,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英國BBC方程式計出今年比利時可奪世界盃冠軍","createTime":"2018-06-14T03:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T00:03:15.000Z","uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0783abe44f303a8a9a58bc291325a2ebc41ddbdb","tid":701240,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:42:40.000Z","msg":"2018俄羅斯世界盃決賽周今晚展開首場賽事，那支球隊是奪冠熱門自是眾說紛紜，各家各法。英國《BBC》就有以下一套方程式，得出冠軍球隊誰屬。<br />\n<br />\n英國《BBC》2018世盃冠軍球隊奪冠方程式&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n1.要是種籽隊<br />\n理據：自從世盃在1998年擴展至32隊，所有冠軍都是種籽隊。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、巴西、葡萄牙、阿根廷、比利時、波蘭、俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n2.不要是主辦國<br />\n理據：由1930至1978年共11屆世盃，主辦國五次奪冠。之後九屆世盃，主辦國只曾一次成為冠軍，就是1998年的法國。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、巴西、葡萄牙、阿根廷、比利時、波蘭<br />\n<br />\n3.防守要好<br />\n理據：自從世盃在1998年擴展至32隊，冠軍隊在七場比賽從未失多於四球。波蘭在外圍賽場均失1.4球，德國、葡萄牙則只失0.4球。另外比利時、法國平均失0.6球，巴西失0.61球，至於阿根廷場均亦只失0.88球。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、巴西、葡萄牙、阿根廷、比利時<br />\n<br />\n4.最好是歐洲球隊<br />\n理據：過往十次在歐洲舉行的世盃，歐洲球隊贏出九次。唯一例外是1958年由巴西奪冠的瑞典世盃。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、葡萄牙、比利時<br />\n<br />\n5.擁有好門將<br />\n理據：近五位世盃金手套得主，其中四人都是世盃冠軍。法國的洛里斯、比利時的泰拔高圖爾斯和德國的紐亞都是非常出色的門將。葡萄牙的魯爾柏迪斯奧明顯被上述三人稍稍比下去。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、比利時<br />\n<br />\n6.有較多國際賽經驗<br />\n理據：國際賽經驗越多的球員，越有利在世盃這種大賽有好發揮。比利時決賽周大軍球員，場均國際賽喼帽為45.13頂，其次為43.26頂喼帽的德國。只得24.56頂國際賽喼帽的法國，是餘下三支球隊中最遜色的一隊。<br />\n結論：德國、比利時<br />\n<br />\n7.不要是衛冕球隊<br />\n理據：自從巴西在1958和1962年連奪世盃冠軍後，再無球隊能夠衛冕世盃。<br />\n結論：比利時"},{"pid":"db784b0910da3a8ea0382f25486d691ec7b6b1b8","tid":701240,"uid":100442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"allin"},{"pid":"3bda4636eaf4338ae2246bcac9155e5634f6fa78","tid":701240,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b766d599d50ae8f0e134a621914cc6834aaae247","tid":701240,"uid":177089,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3bda4636eaf4338ae2246bcac9155e5634f6fa78","tid":701240,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"電腦分析 14%係德國 82%係比利時 4%係荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0100ae0ec4e8e91dbc2e4b573420f7fb1c3d7e61","tid":701240,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfd32ad99c1fa47a854aa6843bfabdb8c5a9f528","tid":701240,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bbc"},{"pid":"742921f3a31676e3d40d78b434b158b62ad38985","tid":701240,"uid":26708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bda4636eaf4338ae2246bcac9155e5634f6fa78","tid":701240,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"佢要前一round 第6輪淨返球隊再揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29084c5887b9e91f2cb78d1788e1ae30200dcb4f","tid":701240,"uid":143086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b766d599d50ae8f0e134a621914cc6834aaae247","tid":701240,"uid":177089,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3bda4636eaf4338ae2246bcac9155e5634f6fa78","tid":701240,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"電腦分析 14%係德國 82%係比利時 4%係荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"開個英格蘭比佢，等佢贏夠100蚊"},{"pid":"2c219a83dea84508bc145610cd869456e3d898dd","tid":701240,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87ade6d57be6d2d02edbdde833ae7351a3b8a15e","tid":701240,"uid":130448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:01:12.000Z","msg":"8 只有與球隊相同國籍教練帶才會奪冠<br />\n完"},{"pid":"f014cb6cfd20de0316f30a1b05abe61c9e5e553a","tid":701240,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"四強：法德葡比<br />\n決賽：德國比利時"},{"pid":"5bde3cc06b1525d2354e5063343b807fa1447037","tid":701240,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ff906a33f073998aae0f40748c9e53295d0e1b","tid":701240,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"4.個例外係巴西但係巴西比人foul走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad67ff739714804828208a92f5f05035d89561b","tid":701240,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"呢d叫方程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7584d37b92d387337a51e5fafe632732b28596","tid":701240,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"西班牙呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46d097728e4041569e2b536e27e622887fdf8df","tid":701240,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"不要是衛冕球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4e0104159b8d830bf31f254f298c43de16c4c0","tid":701240,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"4b970a93931ab78bf94bf2e3a7e22f888e5ee9a2","tid":701240,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/184232_13efeac9dc44d423479a2f8f5d7595c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F184232_13efeac9dc44d423479a2f8f5d7595c5.png&h=93199986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9435b76f23c52a5cd303b504e41587d6651b29a","tid":701240,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:47:11.000Z","msg":"西班牙無了"},{"pid":"625fe437acd61d23e880353400725fc7d29dbc49","tid":701240,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"睇到最好是歐洲球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c103050790b283418382b92c12b54e650de4ea3f","tid":701240,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">On撚柒9<br />\n柏迪斯奧點會差過古圖斯同羅利斯<br />\n尤其呢一兩季<br />\n<br />\n利申 2016年uefa官方搞嗰個全年最佳陣容選擇 門將揀咗柏迪斯奧</span>"},{"pid":"a67b60f6f3446c7f92d60c959424f0437c54eb91","tid":701240,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"2018俄羅斯世界盃決賽周今晚展開首場賽事，那支球隊是奪冠熱門自是眾說紛紜，各家各法。英國《BBC》就有以下一套方程式，得出冠軍球隊誰屬。<br />\n<br />\n英國《BBC》2018世盃冠軍球隊奪冠方程式&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n1.要是種籽隊<br />\n理據：自從世盃在1998年擴展至32隊，所有冠軍都是種籽隊。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、巴西、葡萄牙、阿根廷、比利時、波蘭、俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n2.不要是主辦國<br />\n理據：由1930至1978年共11屆世盃，主辦國五次奪冠。之後九屆世盃，主辦國只曾一次成為冠軍，就是1998年的法國。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、巴西、葡萄牙、阿根廷、比利時、波蘭<br />\n<br />\n3.防守要好<br />\n理據：自從世盃在1998年擴展至32隊，冠軍隊在七場比賽從未失多於四球。波蘭在外圍賽場均失1.4球，德國、葡萄牙則只失0.4球。另外比利時、法國平均失0.6球，巴西失0.61球，至於阿根廷場均亦只失0.88球。<br />\n結論：法國、德國、巴西、葡萄牙、阿根廷、比利時<br />\n<br />\n4.最好是間條球衣<br />\n理據：近年奪冠國家都不是間條波衫， 是時候破例了。<br />\n結論：阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n5.擁有好球員<br />\n理據：五次金球得主及今年歐洲神射手:美斯<br />\n結論：阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n6.有較多國際賽決賽經驗<br />\n理據：國際賽決賽經驗愈多， 在世界盃這種大賽賽事的表現愈好，阿根廷於近年先後闖進世界盃決賽及美洲盃決賽，可惜都飲恨而回，這次阿根廷必定破釜沉舟。<br />\n結論：阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n7.不要是衛冕球隊<br />\n理據： 上屆世界盃阿根廷只得亞軍<br />\n結論：阿根廷"},{"pid":"a2a3a492ed3f374e789b3b14591f076eaca84a21","tid":701240,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f014cb6cfd20de0316f30a1b05abe61c9e5e553a","tid":701240,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"四強：法德葡比<br />\n決賽：德國比利時"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T23:54:20.000Z","msg":"德國呢？"},{"pid":"dccf2a91acc4406aa916136cc357fae87de2e43a","tid":701240,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2a3a492ed3f374e789b3b14591f076eaca84a21","tid":701240,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f014cb6cfd20de0316f30a1b05abe61c9e5e553a","tid":701240,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"四強：法德葡比<br />\n決賽：德國比利時"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T23:54:20.000Z","msg":"德國呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:26:41.000Z","msg":"走線到下屆<br />\n<br />\n華麗隔屆衛冕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3737f495f47d17c5130937f4485e8a00aba7c416","tid":701240,"uid":3017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bda4636eaf4338ae2246bcac9155e5634f6fa78","tid":701240,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}